Jese Rodriguez says he spoke to former Real Madrid teammate Cristiano Ronaldo ahead of his loan move to Sporting Lisbon from Paris Saint-Germain.<br />
<br />
Asked about his conversation with Ronaldo, he said: &quot;He told me it was a very important club for him, he has a lot of affection for Sporting CP. He spoke very well about Sporting.&quot;

